That's why it's bumpy.

651
00:20:54,907 --> 00:20:55,987
It'll only be bumpy in the sea.

652
00:20:56,147 --> 00:20:56,427
Yeah.

653
00:20:59,827 --> 00:21:01,627
The Cromwell town where we are now

654
00:21:01,627 --> 00:21:03,427
was once a major mining town

655
00:21:03,427 --> 00:21:04,947
born from the gold rush.

656
00:21:04,947 --> 00:21:06,027
Due to the construction of a dam,

657
00:21:06,027 --> 00:21:07,347
the original commercial center here

658
00:21:07,347 --> 00:21:08,667
was submerged at the bottom
of a man-made lake.

659
00:21:09,347 --> 00:21:10,907
(Cromwell is a historic heritage town in New Zealand)
The old buildings we see now

660
00:21:10,907 --> 00:21:13,387
(It shows New Zealand's pioneering era)
were moved here from the original town

661
00:21:13,387 --> 00:21:14,827
for tourists to experience

662
00:21:14,827 --> 00:21:16,867
the gold rush history
of the 19th century.

663
00:21:16,867 --> 00:21:18,067
Today's Cromwell

664
00:21:18,067 --> 00:21:20,907
