fruit growing industry.

665
00:21:20,907 --> 00:21:23,107
It's known
as the "Fruit Bowl of the South"

666
00:21:23,107 --> 00:21:24,987
and the "Gateway to Queenstown".

667
00:21:25,427 --> 00:21:27,467
