671
00:21:32,640 --> 00:21:33,267
(Lemon Queen Chase)

672
00:21:33,267 --> 00:21:34,187
There are two groups of four people.

673
00:21:34,187 --> 00:21:35,627
Each person carries a balloon.

674
00:21:36,307 --> 00:21:38,747
Each group designates
one "Lemon Queen" internally.

675
00:21:38,747 --> 00:21:40,627
Pop the opposing team's
balloon of "Lemon Queen",

676
00:21:40,627 --> 00:21:41,547
and you win.

677
00:21:41,547 --> 00:21:42,627
If you attack the wrong person,

678
00:21:42,627 --> 00:21:43,507
the attacker is eliminated.

679
00:21:44,307 --> 00:21:45,267
So, it's actually still a game

680
00:21:45,947 --> 00:21:47,307
