01:01:53,867 --> 01:01:54,987
I said I was on a blind date.

1913
01:01:54,987 --> 01:01:56,347
You said, "With whom?"

1914
01:01:58,267 --> 01:01:59,267
(Chatting away)
Who chased girls?

1915
01:01:59,267 --> 01:01:59,987
Chased who?

1916
01:01:59,987 --> 01:02:00,747
Who in our class?

1917
01:02:03,307 --> 01:02:05,067
Why am I so gossipy?

1918
01:02:08,147 --> 01:02:10,187
Today, in our Heartbeat Journey,
we experienced

1919
01:02:10,187 --> 01:02:12,427
mutual encouragement,
unity, and cooperation,

1920
01:02:12,427 --> 01:02:14,587
and amidst laughter,
we once again enhanced

1921
01:02:14,587 --> 01:02:17,147
the bond between
the Earth Group family members.

1922
01:02:17,147 --> 01:02:19,827
Tomorrow, we will take on
even more difficult challenges

1923
01:02:19,827 --> 01:02:22,427
that require more encouragement
and tacit understanding between you all.

1924
01:02:22,427 --> 01:02:23,987
Let's look forward together

1925
01:02:23,987 --> 01:02:26,067
to tomorrow's Extreme Journey.

1926
01:02:26,587 --> 01:02:27,227
Good night.

1927
01:02:27,227 --> 01:02:28,867
Goodbye.

1928
01:02:29,827 --> 01:02:30,347
Great work.

1929
01:02:44,387 --> 01:02:45,787
(Next Episode Preview)
Seven-Second Heartbeat Word Guessing.

1930
01:02:45,787 --> 01:02:47,227
With Lin Yi, they can't win.

1931
01:02:47,227 --> 01:02:48,307
Trust me.

1932
01:02:48,307 --> 01:02:49,547
I have an extremely high play IQ.

1933
01:02:49,547 --> 01:02:51,387
But today is my home ground.

1934
01:02:52,667 --> 01:02:55,067
I want you to instantly jump up
on your right foot

1935
01:02:55,067 --> 01:02:55,867
to copy my previous move.

1936
01:02:55,867 --> 01:02:56,667
Then go "hehe"

1937
01:02:56,667 --> 01:02:57,747
and tilt your head.

1938
01:02:57,827 --> 01:02:58,587
You still can't guess it?

1939
01:02:59,427 --> 01:03:00,867
The audience has already guessed it.

1940
01:03:00,867 --> 01:03:02,227
And you still haven't.

1941
01:03:03,008 --> 01:03:03,947
(It's your turn)

1942
01:03:03,947 --> 01:03:04,627
A big scoop.

1943
01:03:04,627 --> 01:03:05,427
Then a big scoop.

1944
01:03:05,427 --> 01:03:06,627
Then open your hands and laugh.

1945
01:03:06,627 --> 01:03:07,387
Okay.

1946
01:03:07,387 --> 01:03:07,907
Done scooping.

1947
01:03:08,587 --> 01:03:09,307
What is he doing?

1948
01:03:09,787 --> 01:03:11,307
Do you still think it's simple,

1949
01:03:11,307 --> 01:03:11,867
Yuning?

1950
01:03:11,867 --> 01:03:12,587
I know this one.

1951
01:03:12,587 --> 01:03:13,587
But what is it?

1952
01:03:18,467 --> 01:03:20,896
♪Maybe let's just forget it♪

1953
01:03:21,987 --> 01:03:23,616
It's really quite fun.

1954
01:03:24,027 --> 01:03:24,827
(The soul has left the body)
Say something.

1955
01:03:24,827 --> 01:03:25,387
What's wrong?

1956
01:03:25,387 --> 01:03:26,267
Wake up.

1957
01:03:26,267 --> 01:03:27,107
Fine, I'll jump.

1958
01:03:27,107 --> 01:03:27,616
Come on.

1959
01:03:27,707 --> 01:03:28,832
Just don't look down.

1960
01:03:30,787 --> 01:03:31,827
I'm starting to regret this a bit.

1961
01:03:34,147 --> 01:03:35,187
This is really a bit scary.

1962
01:03:35,232 --> 01:03:36,427
(Stay tuned for the Earth Group's
extreme experience)

1963
01:03:36,427 --> 01:03:37,707
Each team will act

1964
01:03:37,707 --> 01:03:40,256
as an a cappella choir.

1965
01:03:40,256 --> 01:03:40,947
We are bound to win.

1966
01:03:40,947 --> 01:03:42,827
I like their baffling confidence.

1967
01:03:42,827 --> 01:03:44,427
Can four people pull it off?

1968
01:03:48,067 --> 01:03:49,387
Glory or disgrace rests on this battle.

1969
01:03:49,387 --> 01:03:50,707
Ladies and gentlemen,

1970
01:03:50,707 --> 01:03:53,056
the excitement is about to begin.

1971
01:03:54,912 --> 01:03:56,832
(The a cappella showdown
is about to begin)

1972
01:03:57,307 --> 01:04:00,227
This time, we are starting
the Romantic Journey in Paris.

1973
01:04:00,907 --> 01:04:02,307
Welcome the all-around ace,

1974
01:04:02,307 --> 01:04:03,307
Ms. Song Qian.

1975
01:04:04,427 --> 01:04:06,187
This title sets the bar
a bit high for me.

1976
01:04:06,187 --> 01:04:07,467
Whisper Word Guessing.

1977
01:04:07,467 --> 01:04:08,067
You smell.

1978
01:04:08,067 --> 01:04:08,947
Spray something.

1979
01:04:08,947 --> 01:04:09,907
A kind of breakfast.

1980
01:04:10,147 --> 01:04:11,136
A group of what?

1981
01:04:11,387 --> 01:04:12,267
- I hear a sound here.
- Who?

1982
01:04:12,267 --> 01:04:13,184
There's something.

1983
01:04:13,507 --> 01:04:14,187
What did you guess?

1984
01:04:14,467 --> 01:04:15,267
I'm stopping him here.

1985
01:04:15,267 --> 01:04:16,507
Wait, how can you guys play this game

1986
01:04:16,507 --> 01:04:17,547
so badly?

1987
01:04:17,547 --> 01:04:19,107
His description only had one sentence.

1988
01:04:19,107 --> 01:04:19,827
Keep going,

1989
01:04:19,827 --> 01:04:21,227
and my IQ would be too low.

1990
01:04:21,227 --> 01:04:22,467
I've experienced all these things.

1991
01:04:22,467 --> 01:04:23,427
Where is this?

1992
01:04:23,427 --> 01:04:24,347
Notre-Dame de Paris.

1993
01:04:25,147 --> 01:04:26,067
Quite spectacular.

1994
01:04:27,387 --> 01:04:29,147
Now we've reached the top
of Notre-Dame de Paris.

1995
01:04:29,427 --> 01:04:30,067
This is it.

1996
01:04:30,067 --> 01:04:30,787
The spire.

1997
01:04:31,427 --> 01:04:31,867
What is this?

1998
01:04:31,867 --> 01:04:32,827
Is this the Seine River?

1999
01:04:32,827 --> 01:04:33,587
The Seine River.

2000
01:04:34,707 --> 01:04:35,587
The Seine River bank.

2001
01:04:35,587 --> 01:04:37,187
These are Île Saint-Louis
and Île de la Cité.

2002
01:04:39,587 --> 01:04:40,467
So many people.

2003
01:04:41,267 --> 01:04:42,827
Paris at sunset.

2004
01:04:42,827 --> 01:04:44,107
The next game

2005
01:04:44,107 --> 01:04:44,627
is

2006
01:04:44,627 --> 01:04:45,067
a little related

2007
01:04:45,067 --> 01:04:46,387
to acting.

2008
01:04:46,387 --> 01:04:47,907
You didn't expect me
to come so quickly, did you?

2009
01:04:47,907 --> 01:04:48,947
This matter has nothing to do with her.

2010
01:04:48,947 --> 01:04:50,507
This matter is absolutely because of me.

2011
01:04:50,507 --> 01:04:51,107
Mom,

2012
01:04:51,107 --> 01:04:51,787
no, I mean, ma'am.

2013
01:04:51,787 --> 01:04:53,147
She is the woman I love most.

2014
01:04:53,147 --> 01:04:53,947
It's you?

2015
01:04:53,947 --> 01:04:54,907
Why is it you?

2016
01:04:54,907 --> 01:04:55,707
Who is this?

2017
01:04:56,947 --> 01:04:57,547
I don't know him.

2018
01:04:57,547 --> 01:04:58,427
My lady.

2019
01:05:00,027 --> 01:05:01,427
(Secret)
I...

2020
01:05:01,427 --> 01:05:02,587
Wang Yuwen.

2021
01:05:02,587 --> 01:05:03,627
She looks down on us.

2022
01:05:03,627 --> 01:05:04,747
Destroy them.

2023
01:05:04,747 --> 01:05:05,987
How did it suddenly...

2024
01:05:05,987 --> 01:05:07,027
A complete reversal.

2025
01:05:07,799 --> 01:05:08,736
(How will they act it out?)

2026
01:05:08,867 --> 01:05:10,427
(Extra Episode Preview)
Play a round of psychological warfare.

2027
01:05:10,427 --> 01:05:12,227
What if we still win this round? Right?

2028
01:05:12,507 --> 01:05:13,827
That's basically impossible.

2029
01:05:14,347 --> 01:05:15,547
Do you need us to go easy on you?

2030
01:05:15,627 --> 01:05:16,987
Thank you, Yuning, for going easy on us.

2031
01:05:16,987 --> 01:05:17,467
Alright.

2032
01:05:17,907 --> 01:05:19,227
Don't lose too fast, okay?

2033
01:05:21,107 --> 01:05:21,907
Come out.

2034
01:05:21,907 --> 01:05:22,987
Come over here.

2035
01:05:23,147 --> 01:05:24,107
Is it you?

2036
01:05:28,307 --> 01:05:29,856
Stop arguing, guys.

2037
01:05:29,856 --> 01:05:31,267
Make your move.

2038
01:05:33,343 --> 01:05:35,008
(Which group will win?)

2039
01:05:35,008 --> 01:05:36,867
(Special Extra Episode Preview)
Everyone, give yourself

2040
01:05:36,867 --> 01:05:38,947
a new name too.

2041
01:05:38,947 --> 01:05:41,307
Then I want to be called
"Potato Mound Calf".

2042
01:05:41,307 --> 01:05:42,987
I'm called "Four Yili Horses
Outside the Door".

2043
01:05:42,987 --> 01:05:44,387
You can pick whichever two you want.

2044
01:05:44,387 --> 01:05:46,227
I'm called Sun Honglei.

2045
01:05:46,227 --> 01:05:47,427
I'm called Li Naiwen.

2046
01:05:47,427 --> 01:05:48,707
Don't call yourself Li Naiwen.
It's bad luck.

2047
01:05:48,707 --> 01:05:49,947
I'm called Guo Jingfei.

2048
01:05:49,947 --> 01:05:50,947
Even worse luck.

2049
01:05:50,947 --> 01:05:52,107
Let's go by age.

2050
01:05:52,107 --> 01:05:53,568
You must find one person to watch.

2051
01:05:53,568 --> 01:05:55,187
Then it's enough for me
to watch one person.

2052
01:05:55,187 --> 01:05:56,747
You want to eliminate seven in one go?

2053
01:05:56,747 --> 01:05:58,267
How many rooms
do you want to live in alone?

2054
01:05:58,267 --> 01:06:00,547
Three, two, one.

2055
01:06:00,576 --> 01:06:01,440
(Who will win in the end?)

2056
01:06:01,787 --> 01:06:05,027
The first meeting
between both sets of parents.

2057
01:06:05,027 --> 01:06:05,467
Sister-in-law.

2058
01:06:05,667 --> 01:06:06,547
Younger brother.

2059
01:06:06,627 --> 01:06:07,467
Grandson.

2060
01:06:07,747 --> 01:06:10,496
The other side is a bit noisy.

2061
01:06:10,587 --> 01:06:11,747
This is my first blind date.

2062
01:06:11,747 --> 01:06:12,747
I'm a bit nervous.

2063
01:06:12,747 --> 01:06:14,107
Aren't we about to get married?

2064
01:06:14,107 --> 01:06:15,267
You scumbag!

2065
01:06:15,267 --> 01:06:15,947
What do you mean?

2066
01:06:15,947 --> 01:06:17,347
You two were even love rivals before?

2067
01:06:17,347 --> 01:06:18,720
(How will they act it out?)

2068
01:06:19,138 --> 01:06:49,376
(Wow The World, show schedule)
